mikro-dns (0.1.0-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Complete DNS record management
  * Support for A, AAAA, CNAME, MX, TXT, NS, SRV, FWD, REGEXP, NXDOMAIN
  * Search, validate, import/export functionality
  * Role-based access control
  * All configuration managed by mikro-common

